The '''Central Gathering Hall''' was a building in [[Galactic City/Legends|Imperial City]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] with a large [[Chronometer/Legends|clock]]. It would send a ripple of light into the night sky to mark the hour. By the time of the [[Thrawn campaign]], it had been functioning thus for roughly [[291 BBY|three centuries]].

